ext":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"orifice of the rectum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"orifice of the vagina."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10787","headword_ar":"خَصَفَةٌ","root":"xSf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A receptacle for dates, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~ap","text_ar":"جُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of palm-leaves;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wherein they are stored:"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dial. of El-Bahreyn: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mat upon which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqiT","text_ar":"اَقِط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c. are put to dry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$r","text_ar":"شر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and [it is said to signify]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a very thick kind of cloth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSafN","text_ar":"خَصَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) [or rather this is a coll. gen. n.,] and [the pl. properly speaking is]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSaAfN","text_ar":"خِصَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) Lth says that a certain Tubba' [a king of El-Yemen] clothed the House [i. e. the Kaabeh] with ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaf","text_ar":"خَصَف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very thick cloths;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so called as being likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaf","text_ar":"خَصَف"},{"kind":"text","text":"of woven palm-leaves: but Az says that this is wrong; and that it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of matting made of palm-leaves woven together, oblong pieces of which were used as coverings for the tents of the Arabs of the desert, and sometimes made into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilaAl","text_ar":"جِلَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~apN","text_ar":"جُلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for dates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuS~aAfN","text_ar":"خُصَّافٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of matting of palm-leaves;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASiyfu","text_ar":"خَصَاصِيفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","Lth"]}]}}